            <title>[CASSANDRA-16777] Flaky ViewTest</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-16777</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;ViewTest has been &lt;a href=&quot;https://ci-cassandra.apache.org/job/Cassandra-4.0/113/testReport/junit/org.apache.cassandra.cql3/ViewTest/testFrozenCollectionsWithComplicatedInnerType/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;failing&lt;/a&gt; every now and then on the 4.0 line. Being so close to having 0 faky failures I want to scratch that itch so I propose we split it like we did with ViewComplexTest.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
